{"tid":2204722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"YooA拿一位爆哭！Oh my girl隊長跳上舞台幫伴舞　深厚感情看哭粉絲","createTime":"2020-09-16T09:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:26:04.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"15b81bae8e2447983b8127940fdda228913a4e87","tid":2204722,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:18:09.000Z","msg":"南韓女團Oh my girl透過節目《Queendom》累積知名度與人氣，7位成員齊攜手熬過低潮期，現如今迎來，累積出好感情。近日，隊內成員YooA成為團體裡第一位個人出輯的人，她化身森林系仙子，挑戰高難度舞蹈與歌曲，實力也獲得認證，15日拿下音樂節目《The Show》一位冠軍，在發表感言時，講著講著突然喜極而泣，為了給予她鼓勵，隊長效定戴著口罩跳上舞台安慰她，最後加入舞伴一起跳舞，團體間深厚的情誼溢於言表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5144/d5144195.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5144%2Fd5144195.jpg&h=3de3068e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼YooA拿一位爆哭，Oh my girl效定跳上舞台給予安慰，開心地拍手狂跳，深厚感情看哭粉絲。（圖／翻攝自《The Show》）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5144/d5144197.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5144%2Fd5144197.jpg&h=7fc601f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYooA於15日拿下音樂節目《The Show》一位冠軍，她在講感言時，拿著麥克風就已經開始哽咽，並表示自己是成員間第一個solo的人，「謝謝大家給予的喜愛，用心地準備了舞台表演帶給粉絲們，沒有料想到會得獎，能夠獲得一位心情很開心。」感言尾聲，她不忘感謝粉絲與Oh my girl。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5144/d5144199.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5144%2Fd5144199.jpg&h=6a4c13c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲效定在舞台上加入舞群伴舞，最後貼心地默默退出舞台。（圖／翻攝自《The Show》）<br />\n<br />\nYooA在台上喜極而泣，隊長效定見狀立刻在安可時跳上舞台，給予她一個大大的擁抱，隨後為她拭去臉上的眼淚，接著開心到在旁邊跟著手舞足蹈拍手、跳舞，最後貼心地默默退出舞台，這段影片曝光後，粉絲紛紛留言表示「連我看都要哭了」、「效定太可愛了」、「Oh my girl感情真好」。<br />\n<br />\n定姐姐都幾弱智。。。"},{"pid":"328942d603554ad94e8b2a307521b664dee7eb93","tid":2204722,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40583d8ee66d977729639cd163664a518480cd9","tid":2204722,"uid":89931,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定姐姐。。。"},{"pid":"2ea38cb0ac7c56c8c8f37c2a5e0b23b856612c42","tid":2204722,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"隊長又有冇係鏡頭面前爆哭？"},{"pid":"e14611b2809e953758d0e4fcc219c87856b26d5e","tid":2204722,"uid":251328,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"唔係嘛 ！ CLC仲要輸埋俾1個啱啱出嚟solo嘅女團成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要係the show個啲垃圾1位都拎唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌⋯⋯癈撚到咁就快啲解散好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37ac9c4670db0d15e525f65819a81660de25388","tid":2204722,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T10:08:37.000Z","msg":"@<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你嘅定兒😳"},{"pid":"f907a68f9ff2a88782ed802f4c4f142645edfed2","tid":2204722,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"屌...."},{"pid":"42929dba619c1ea895da187dee91a4b0ee74f3d1","tid":2204722,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc57a1c1128bae097ae3c2ae13a8dc26b282f10","tid":2204722,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14611b2809e953758d0e4fcc219c87856b26d5e","tid":2204722,"uid":251328,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,